  {
    "hero": "Domina",
    "ID": "e2ccc17bc24510e63222ca4a945334b3",
    "line": "Expand *sigh* Tum mujhe paa nahin sakte. (Hindi) Devanagari: तुम मुझे पा नहीं सकते। English: You can't afford me. (Literally: You can't attain me.)",
